ActControlled Drugs and Substances Act
SubjectOrder Amending Schedule lll to the Controlled Drugs and Substances Act (Aminorex)
PrecisOrder Amending SCHEDULE III TO THE CONTROLLED DRUGS AND SUBSTANCES ACT (AMINOREX) in order to fulfil Canada’s international obligation under the 1971 Convention to control 4,4’-Dimethylaminorex under the Controlled Drugs and Substances Act, and to protect the health and safety of Canadians from the risk of problematic use of related New Psychoactive Substance that may emerge in the future.
